Simple gun game map that I had made. took me a while to make because i've been having problems with pakrat for months now. Though now i will be releasing more maps, not tons but more in future.  

Side note to add: the grey platforms that you see between the red and white platforms actually lift you up when you stand on them, making gameplay a bit more fun; using it as cover, mobility and sneak kills.
